01:55.600 --> 02:07.120
can find. I began combing the magazine markets looking at the mundane
periodicals. In Liberty Magazine occasionally I found something new by H.G.

02:07.300 --> 02:19.380
Wells or Saks Romer with his Fu Manchu super scientific villain. And in the
pages of Argosy I discovered that this magazine, besides having westerns and

02:19.380 --> 02:30.360
romance and air war and whatnot, that they generally had some science fiction
